## client hash
+ hash方案：[CryptoJS-sha265](https://cryptojs.gitbook.io/docs/)
>>>md5 是否安全的讨论 https://stackoverflow.com/questions/4032209/is-md5-still-good-enough-to-uniquely-identify-files
+ [Web Browser: File Read API](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/FileReader/FileReader#examples)

核心代码：
```ts
async function getFileHash(file, {
  CryptoJS = null,
  cbProgress = null,
  algo = 'SHA256',
  encoding = 'Base64url',
  chunkSize = 1 * 1024 * 1024,
} = {}) {
  if (!CryptoJS)
    return Promise.reject(new Error('crypto-js module not provided'))

  if (!CryptoJS.algo.hasOwnProperty(algo))
    return Promise.reject(new Error('Given hash algo not supported'))

  if (!['Base64', 'Base64url', 'Hex'].includes(encoding))
    return Promise.reject(new Error(`Given hash encoding not supported. Supported encodings are "Base64", "Base64url", "Hex"`))

  return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
    const hashObj = CryptoJS.algo[algo].create()
    const fileSize = file.size
    let offset = 0

    const reader = new FileReader()
    reader.onload = function () {
      if (reader.error)
        return reject(reader.error)

      hashObj.update(CryptoJS.enc.Latin1.parse(reader.result))

      offset += reader.result.length
      if (cbProgress)
        cbProgress(offset / fileSize)

      if (offset >= fileSize) {
        const hash = hashObj.finalize()
        const hashHex = hash.toString(CryptoJS.enc[encoding])
        return resolve(hashHex)
      }
      readNext()
    }

    reader.onerror = function (err) {
      reject(err)
    }

    function readNext() {
      const fileSlice = file.slice(offset, offset + chunkSize)
      reader.readAsBinaryString(fileSlice)
    }
    readNext()
  })
}
```
> 详细 Github 参考 [点击此处](https://github.com/shancwovo/vue-sandbox/commit/aabea840334af478f85e38cd5acda5166d3be87b)

## client 文件切分上传 & server 组装

> web端使用fetch API 获取 input 的file chunk 并直接上传，server 使用nodejs 起http server，接收拼接chunk。web端上传完毕后，主动告诉server 需要进行合并。

使用的重要API：
+ fetch:[[frontend/is formdata necessary in http file upload\|is formdata necessary in http file upload]]
+ node:fs
	+ createReadStream：读取chunk
	+ createWriteStream：持续写入chunk
	+ unlinkSync: 删除chunk
+ node:http：简单的http server
### 代码示意：
source code: [feat: ✨ 大文件切分上传](https://github.com/shancwovo/vue-sandbox/commit/9e976da3910f2a0c68e45cbcb57c5302c29e021d)
client(vue)：
```jsx
// input
<input ref="fileRef" type="file">
// functions



function upload() {
  const file = fileRef.value.files[0]
  const fileSize = file.size

  let index = 0
  let offset = 0
  const chunkSize = 1 * 1024 * 1024

  function readNext() {
    if (offset < fileSize) {
      const fileSlice = file.slice(offset, offset + chunkSize)

      fetch('/fileService/upload', {
        method: 'post',
        body: fileSlice,
        headers: {
          'x-file-name': `${file.name}`,
          'x-file-index': index,
        },
      })
        .then(res => res.text())
        .then(() => {
          index += 1
          offset += chunkSize
          readNext()
        })
    }
    else {
      fetch('/fileService/compose', {
        method: 'post',
        body: JSON.stringify({
          name: file.name,
          total: index,
        }),
      })
    }
  }
  readNext()
}
```
server(simple node http):
```js
function composeFile() {
    let data = ''
    req.on('data', (chunk) => {
      data += chunk
    })
    req.on('end', async () => {
      const { name, total } = JSON.parse(data)

      const tempFilePath = path.join(process.cwd(), name)
      if (fs.existsSync(tempFilePath)) {
        const uploadPath = path.join(process.cwd(), 'uploads')
        mkdirIfNotExist(uploadPath)
        const writeStream = fs.createWriteStream(`${uploadPath}/${name}`)

        mergeCore(0, total)

        function mergeCore(mergedChunkNum, total) {
          if (mergedChunkNum >= total)
            return
          const chunkPath = path.join(tempFilePath, (mergedChunkNum).toString())
          const chunkReadStream = fs.createReadStream(chunkPath)
          chunkReadStream.pipe(writeStream, { end: false })

          chunkReadStream.on('end', () => {
            fs.unlinkSync(chunkPath)
            mergeCore(mergedChunkNum + 1, total)
          })
        }
      }
    })
  }

  function cacheFile() {
    // 处理文件上传请求
    const chunks = []
    let totalSize = 0

    req.on('data', (chunk) => {
      chunks.push(chunk)
      totalSize += chunk.length
    })

    req.on('end', () => {
      // 将所有接收到的数据拼接起来
      const data = Buffer.concat(chunks, totalSize)

      // 获取文件名
      const fileName = path.basename(req.headers['x-file-name'])

      const filePath = path.join(process.cwd(), fileName)

      mkdirIfNotExist(filePath)

      // 写入文件

      fs.writeFile(path.join(filePath, req.headers['x-file-index']), data, (err) => {
        if (err) {
          res.writeHead(500, { 'Content-Type': 'text/plain' })
          res.end('Internal Server Error')
        }
        else {
          res.writeHead(200, { 'Content-Type': 'text/plain' })
          res.end('File uploaded successfully')
        }
      })
    })
  }
```
